item.description:
A quick movie review, did Chelsea Clinton tweet her allegiance to the Dark Lord, and then we take a look at the Satanic origins of New Year’s Day on our Hungover New Year’s episode!

Patreon

Help Promote Dead Rabbit!

Dual Flyer
https://i.imgur.com/OhuoI2v.jpg

"As Above" Flyer 
https://i.imgur.com/yobMtUp.jpg

 

“Bird Box” is Netflix’s newest hyped hit. Is it ready to take flight? Or should this have been one of the two birds that got hit by the stone? I know, I know, that was lame.

Then we check out the Twitter feed of Chelsea Clinton. Is there any truth to the rumor that she tweeted “Happy New Year” to the Church of Satan?

And finally we take a look at the satanic origins of New Year’s Day traditions. Is the Lord Of Lies ready to strike every January 1st?
